===Noun===
[[Image:halo-halo1.JPG|left|thumb|150px|The Halo-halo]][[Image:Halo-halo2.jpg|thumb|left|100px|Another variation of the Halo-halo]]
Halo-Halo - /hăl-ŏ - hăl-ŏ/ is a popular Filipino dessert which literally means, "mix-mix." A tall glass is filled with: shaved ice, milk (or coconut milk), coconut sport, a dash of crema de ube and leche flan, sweetened plantains, jackfruit, and topped with a scoop of your favorite ice cream.